{"tid":1192351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"容我再次呼籲：香港或將告終，但我們六九不散","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:36:08.000Z","uid":85612,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"70b9fee46b05f5b1446b0feaa51ad9a3c4858c4f","tid":1192351,"uid":85612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"可以預期港府自殺式修例「成功」之後<br />\n寒蟬效應，自我審查等怪現象會插水式惡化<br />\n香港僅餘嘅言論自由、法治行將消失<br />\n只講搵食嘅香港人，好快連私有產權同人身安全依兩條底線都保唔住<br />\n無咗以上種種，金融等第三產業一定全線收皮<br />\n香港工業、科技，旅遊又落後於廣州、深圳同澳門<br />\n當香港唔再係國際金融中心，係大灣區仲有咩利用價值？<br />\n係高度發達嘅珠三角，連做唔做到大陸二線城市都成問題。<br />\n到時真係大規模走資，結構性失業<br />\n香港人自然用腳投票，end of the HK story<br />\n而家已經可能係香港作為國際級城市最後嘅幾年<br />\n估唔到連登仔等唔到支爆來臨，香港已經玩完<br />\n我唔想再多講啲咩<br />\n香港已到存亡之時，今次唔再係泛民個種「民主最黑暗一日」<br />\n而係真正嘅，從社會、經濟嘅全面自毀、解離同國際地位嘅消亡<br />\n而係依個時候，歐美國家似乎有心關注香港事務<br />\n係依個歷史性時刻<br />\n唔理你自問係香港人、中國人、中國香港人、英屬香港遺民，甚至已經係外國人都好<br />\n計形勢計風險成本，今次可能會係你最後仲肯考慮行出嚟，出嚟行嘅一次<br />\n既然係咁，請真係出嚟，犧牲多少少<br />\n無論係出嚟表達不滿，想抗爭到底，慣咗每年遊行，想出嚟睇熱鬧，想行埋依次做個紀念又好<br />\n今次請你務必，務必出現，最好帶多幾個人嚟，一齊遊行，一齊聚集，用中國嘅講法，「發出最後的吼聲」<br />\n因為作為香港人，咁樣嘅機會，以及咁樣嘅城市，以後好可能都唔會再有了。<br />\n集會人數愈多，國際社會愈有關注<br />\n香港或終將起落有時，但香港人六九不散。"},{"pid":"347cc0d934a08462fcc3fafe6e89e0495181f88a","tid":1192351,"uid":28366,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/PoliticalVigorousHousefly-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FPoliticalVigorousHousefly-size_restricted.gif&h=41e34efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62013711_659215344521877_1086940503313743872_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=12470952d62fcbd0e5fc1c4e9fee3127&amp;oe=5D99AB8B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62013711_659215344521877_1086940503313743872_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D12470952d62fcbd0e5fc1c4e9fee3127%26oe%3D5D99AB8B&h=ca0db275&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"402294f5b7056a76f72d8ec1a752b022ef240e31","tid":1192351,"uid":52230,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\n不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a0f9182dbe4e92de8d700be9074ec0ceb6637e","tid":1192351,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"[雨傘的教訓] 必須反守為攻 一鼓作氣 佔路無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cJwEKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cJwEKS</a>"},{"pid":"f5c44f1197ad0a3283db2670816a3f9cff09b641","tid":1192351,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5983124cd9f5a1326ceb81c12d34a4e211b773e7","tid":1192351,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9639cf8c378aef7341dd0ac354ddd1503718a0e4","tid":1192351,"uid":31749,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:40: